data.description:
BUYERS INCENTIVE: seller offering to pay closing costs AND a home buyers warranty. 
Custom home by Medallion Construction. 
The kitchen is open to the the large family room and the dining room, home office, and half bath complete the main floor. Upstairs you will find all four generously sized bedrooms, including the large master suite with trey ceilings and a 10x10 closet. The laundry room is located upstairs, with washer/dryer included with the home. 
With all of the bedrooms are upstairs, no need to bring laundry up/down the stairs!  This home offers both a front & back covered porch, with the back porch cover extending to a 10x14 concrete patio complete with outdoor fireplace and TV. Perfect for outdoor living and entertaining. Fruit trees planted and bearing fruit already! All mounted TVs included with home. This home has it all including a short walk to downtown harlem and the elementary school. Also, a short drive to Fort Eisenhowers gate 6 entrance! Seller to consider split commission for buyers realtor. Contact owner today for showing!
